                  <handDesc>
                     <summary>Italian semi-cursive script</summary>
                     <handNote>
                        The scribe, who decorated the name <persName>Samuel</persName> many times (e.g. on <locus>fols. 51r, 127v-twice, 133v</locus>), copied <locus>fols. 1-141</locus>. The index (<locus>fols. 143r-147r</locus>), <lang xml:lang="he">עניין ניקור הבשר</lang> (<locus>fol. 147r-147v</locus>), <locus>fols. 148r-159r</locus>, and <locus>fols. 159v-166v</locus> were each copied by a different hand.
                        Censor: <persName key="person_316606361">Camillo Jaghel</persName> 1611 (<locus>fol. 172r</locus>).
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>

